Endovascular stent-graft treatment of aortic dissection: determinants of 
post-interventional outcome.

Eggebrecht H(1), Herold U, Kuhnt O, Schmermund A, Bartel T, Martini S, Lind A, 
Naber CK, Kienbaum P, Kühl H, Peters J, Jakob H, Erbel R, Baumgart D.

Author information:
